      "lesson title": "Building Trust in AI-Assisted Client Services",
      "order": 1,
      "Description": "This lesson introduces the foundational principles of building and maintaining client trust when AI tools are used to support professional services. You will explore what transparency and disclosure mean in practice, including when and how to inform clients that AI has played a role in the work delivered to them. We will examine the ethical responsibilities that come with using AI in client-facing contexts, and how to handle these situations with honesty and professionalism. By the end of this lesson, you will have a clearer understanding of how to communicate openly with clients, set appropriate expectations, and uphold the standards your clients deserve. No prior knowledge of AI is required, and all concepts are explained in straightforward, practical terms.",
